OL,3,CMum speaks of difficulty of three-year
OL,4,Cwait for young son's surgery
OL,6,FA mother has spoken about the
OL,7,Fdifficulty of seeing her son suffer
OL,8,Fafter waiting three years for
OL,9,Ftreatment for obstructive tonsils.
OL,11,FJessi Stephens' four-year-old son
OL,12,FHarris is waiting for a tonsillectomy
OL,13,Fand to have his adenoids removed after
OL,14,Fsuffering with tonsillitis 16 times in
OL,15,Fthe first year of his life.
OL,17,F"He gets really bad tonsillitis a
OL,18,Flot," Jessi told ITV Cymru Wales.
