OL,4,Cwait for young son's surgery
OL,6,FJessi is hoping access to treatment
OL,7,Fwill improve her son's quality of life.
OL,9,F"We really want to just get it done
OL,10,Fand dusted because the recovery is
OL,11,Fgoing to be quite long," she said.
OL,13,F"We just want to get it done so he can
OL,14,Fcontinue being happy, which he is when
OL,15,Fhe's well."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/9
