OL,3,CMum speaks of difficulty of three-year
OL,4,Cwait for young son's surgery
OL,6,F"It's really hard to see your child
OL,7,Fsuffer and to be waiting for something
OL,8,Fyou know is a relatively simple and
OL,9,Feasy procedure. There just doesn't
OL,10,Fseem to be a need for such a long
OL,11,Fwait."
OL,13,FHarris was referred as an urgent case
OL,14,Fafter having tonsillitis 16 times in
OL,15,Fhis first year.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/9
