OL,3,CMum speaks of difficulty of three-year
OL,4,Cwait for young son's surgery
OL,6,F"It's been nearly three full years of
OL,7,Fhim being on an urgent list. His GPs
OL,8,Fare frustrated with it, his other
OL,9,Fconsultants are frustrated, it's been
OL,10,Fwritten up to be expedited many times,
OL,11,Fbut he's just sitting on a list,"
OL,12,FJessi said.
OL,14,FJessi's eldest son also had large
OL,15,Ftonsils and was referred for a
OL,16,Ftonsillectomy after two years of
OL,17,Fwaiting. She said it was affecting his
OL,18,Fbreathing and he ended up having the
OL,19,Ftreatment done privately.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/9
