OL,3,CMum speaks of difficulty of three-year
OL,4,Cwait for young son's surgery
OL,6,F"Instantly, he was better and his
OL,7,Fquality of life was so much better,"
OL,8,Fshe said. "We got the phone call that
OL,9,Fhe was top of the list about a year
OL,10,Fafter he had his tonsils out. So, I
OL,11,Fsaid, 'There's no need, it's done'."
OL,13,FHowever, due to Harris's other health
OL,14,Fconditions, Jessi says they are unable
OL,15,Fto treat him privately.
