OL,3,CMum speaks of difficulty of three-year
OL,4,Cwait for young son's surgery
OL,6,FThe Cabinet Health Secretary Jeremy
OL,7,FMiles said he was "very happy to see a
OL,8,Fsignificant fall in the longest waits
OL,9,Fand the overall size of the waiting
OL,10,Flist falling for the third month in a
OL,11,Frow."
OL,13,FHe added: "We still have more work to
OL,14,Fdo to reach our ambitious targets, but
OL,15,Fit is encouraging to see waiting times
OL,16,Fconsistently falling."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/9
