OL,3,CMum speaks of difficulty of three-year
OL,4,Cwait for young son's surgery
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Cymru Wales, he said:
OL,7,F"I've set the NHS a target that by the
OL,8,Fend of next year, by the end of the
OL,9,FSenedd term, that target of nobody
OL,10,Fwaiting longer than two years will
OL,11,Fhave been met.
OL,13,F"But what we've seen in the last few
OL,14,Fmonths in particular is a laser-like
OL,15,Ffocus right across the NHS, in some of
OL,16,Fthose most challenged specialities -
OL,17,Forthopedics, ophthalmology - the
OL,18,Fnumber of long waits really coming
OL,19,Fdown, some of them have been cut in
OL,20,Fhalf.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/9
